Your source files reside in this directory

relation_model.sql

Explains the relation model in detail.
SQLs written against MySQL db.

top_customer.py

Should be run independently and is self sufficient.
Requires events.txt file as input file containing all the events.
That file is under the sample_input folder in this repository or can be found at
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/coderyogi/code-challenge/master/sample_input/events.txt

The same code can also be found in Google Code Colab at
https://colab.research.google.com/drive/1e1Fz9V76LUW7xEgLafFIYMKX6a0wQqX6

Since this is self sufficient have not including any error handling conditions for graceful exit.


